metadata.name: Where my balloon goes
metadata.description:
Edition title: Where my balloon goes

The little girl is adventurous and full of imagination,  
she discovers new things, simply for the exhilaration.  
Her balloon guides her through life and allows her to fly,  
as the one thing she seeks in this space, is to get H.I.G.H.

Honesty – to yourself and others in your life.  
Integrity – to do the right thing, although it may not be the easy.  
Gratitude – to be thankful for what we have and those around us.  
Humility – to have the freedom from pride or arrogance.

Artists: DracheTech11 & VivianeG
